HEADWORD: Fishlike
<hw>Fish"like</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like fish;
suggestive of fish; having some of the qualities of fish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A very ancient and <qex>fishlike</qex> smell.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

